      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, i'm a trainer working with a pretty diverse group of clients lately. i want to make sure i'm being as effective as possible with my programming. from a sports science perspective, are there actually any biological differences in muscle fiber types or athletic potential between different racial groups that i should be accounting for when i design these programs?",
